src:
RBK-trenerens kone tok imot pris på vegne av mannen: Røpet familiens strategi
01 Nov 2019, 21:20 by Kristina Bye
Eirik Horneland vant én av prisene under årets Idrettens Hederskveld. For første gang inntok kona Tine Horneland scenen for å motta det synlige beviset.
Eirik Horneland vant «Årets pådriverpris» under Idrettens Hederskveld 2019.
text:
The RBK coach's wife welcomed on behalf of the man: Reached the family strategy
01 Nov 2019, 21:20 by Kristina Bye
Eirik Horneland won one of the awards during this year's Sports Honors Night. For the first time, his wife Tine Horneland took the stage to receive the visible evidence.
Eirik Horneland won the "Drivers Award of the Year" during the Sports Honors Night 2019.
